    • Enum Constant Detail

      • BROWSER_NAME

        public static final CapabilityTypes.CommonCapabilityProperties BROWSER_NAME
        Reads property web.driver.capability.browserName and returns string value. Should be the same as following:

        BrowserType.CHROME

        BrowserType.EDGE

        BrowserType.FIREFOX

        BrowserType.IEXPLORE

        BrowserType.OPERA_BLINK

        BrowserType.SAFARI It has sense to define value of the property when value of the property SupportedWebDriverProperty.SUPPORTED_WEB_DRIVER_PROPERTY_PROPERTY is SupportedWebDrivers.REMOTE_DRIVER

      • PLATFORM_NAME

        public static final CapabilityTypes.CommonCapabilityProperties PLATFORM_NAME
        Reads property web.driver.capability.platformName and returns string value. Should be the same as an item of Platform

      • SUPPORTS_JAVASCRIPT

        public static final CapabilityTypes.CommonCapabilityProperties SUPPORTS_JAVASCRIPT
        Reads property web.driver.capability.javascriptEnabled and returns boolean value. Should be true or false. By default it returns true.

      • BROWSER_VERSION

        public static final CapabilityTypes.CommonCapabilityProperties BROWSER_VERSION
        Reads property web.driver.capability.browserVersion and returns string value.
